                                 ->  Redistribute Motion 3:3  (slice3; segments: 3)
                                       Output: ws1.ws_order_number, ws1.ws_warehouse_sk
                                       Hash Key: ws1.ws_order_number
                                       ->  Seq Scan on cte_prune.tpcds_web_sales ws1
