                                                                                                   Hash Cond: (t4_2.d = t3_1.a)
                                                                                                   ->  Redistribute Motion 3:3  (slice6; segments: 3)
                                                                                                         Output: t4_2.d
                                                                                                         Hash Key: t4_2.d
                                                                                                         ->  Seq Scan on cte_prune.t4 t4_2
                                                                                                               Output: t4_2.d
                                                                                                   ->  Hash
                                                                                                         Output: t3_1.a, t3_1.b
                                                                                                         ->  Seq Scan on cte_prune.t3 t3_1
